title: Total Canadian vehicles returning to the country in Canada 2017
summary: The Number of Total Canadian vehicles returning to the country begins at a prominent high level , followed by a dramatical drop to reach the lowest point in April , which reduces to a fifth of the beginning point .
Then the Number remains stable with a slight increase to December .
gold: This graph indicates the number of total Canadian vehicles returning to the country in 2017 . The lowest number of approximately 1400000 can be observed during the month of February . Over the following 4 months a steady increase takes place .
